Write ``dist-info/RECORD`` in UTF-8 instead of platform-dependent
encoding to correctly install wheels containing files with non-ASCII
names. Note that installing from source or sdist may still fail due
to Setuptools not being able to process those file names. See
`pypa/setuptools#1399`_.

.. _`pypa/setuptools#1399`: https://github.com/pypa/setuptools/issues/1399
